1.16.18  11:32 pm   I just got my very humble home recording setup, well, set up. It's been years since I had anything besides a tape recorder and I'm pumped because I immediately felt inspried to start a couple songs! My goal of this year is to write and record a whole album and I plan on playing most if not all of the instruments myself. Do you have any advice or even lips about the process of doing it all yourself?

     i would suggest starting with much smaller projects. getting a brand new system and starting with a large project might be a recipe for disaster.... i think i've seen this before ....
